1
00:00:12,429 --> 00:00:18,435
<i>As far as my eyes can see,
colors abound</i>

2
00:00:18,435 --> 00:00:24,191
<i>Scenes of the past, unravel, unwound</i>

3
00:00:24,191 --> 00:00:29,655
<i>Paradox tightens,
the resolve we've found</i>

4
00:00:29,655 --> 00:00:35,160
<i>Sinking into tomorrows,
out of bounds</i>

5
00:00:35,827 --> 00:00:41,458
<i>If I open these hands,
once clenched tight</i>

6
00:00:41,458 --> 00:00:49,550
<i>I'll grasp at hopes,
long lost from sight</i>

7
00:00:49,550 --> 00:00:55,639
<i>Tears have dried,
facing the darkest night</i>

8
00:00:55,639 --> 00:01:01,812
<i>Even as you gaze at a future bright</i>

9
00:01:01,812 --> 00:01:07,109
<i>Finally, the light, almost within sight</i>

10
00:01:07,109 --> 00:01:11,113
<i>No words needed,
in silence, take flight</i>

11
00:01:11,113 --> 00:01:15,659
<i>For all the answers, here,</i>

12
00:01:15,659 --> 00:01:22,499
<i>in our hands alight</i>

13
00:01:30,007 --> 00:01:32,259
(Episode 12: "And The One She Chooses")

14
00:01:38,807 --> 00:01:40,976
An entity who can kill me, huh...

15
00:01:41,893 --> 00:01:43,312
Maybe you were right.

16
00:01:44,062 --> 00:01:45,397
Maybe that is...

17
00:01:46,231 --> 00:01:48,525
what I have been hoping for all along.

18
00:01:50,110 --> 00:01:50,902
Mio...

19
00:01:52,195 --> 00:01:55,657
I'm not lying about
trying to revive Shin.

20
00:01:56,450 --> 00:02:00,829
I've lived all this time
to see Shin once again.

21
00:02:02,247 --> 00:02:04,374
However, you are right, Shido...

22
00:02:04,374 --> 00:02:10,505
Part of me was wondering, "Is it truly
Shin that was born in that way?"

23
00:02:12,047 --> 00:02:13,070
But...

24
00:02:13,634 --> 00:02:17,179
I didn't know what else to do...

25
00:02:19,765 --> 00:02:22,809
I see, maybe...

26
00:02:22,809 --> 00:02:25,312
I really did want to die all along.

27
00:02:30,442 --> 00:02:33,862
Why didn't I notice
something so simple?

28
00:02:37,491 --> 00:02:42,204
The fact that you kissed me
knowing that much...

29
00:02:43,622 --> 00:02:47,709
You are trying to kill me,
aren't you, Shido?

30
00:02:50,921 --> 00:02:51,713
Yeah...

31
00:02:53,882 --> 00:02:54,716
Did you...

32
00:02:55,467 --> 00:02:56,718
expect me to say that?

33
00:02:58,970 --> 00:03:02,474
I'm sorry, but I don't have
as much guts as you do.

34
00:03:03,141 --> 00:03:05,102
I can't bear your death.

35
00:03:05,894 --> 00:03:07,354
You know, Mio...

36
00:03:07,979 --> 00:03:11,983
I'm here to take you away from Shinji!

37
00:03:14,236 --> 00:03:18,031
I have the ten Sephiras in my body now.

38
00:03:18,031 --> 00:03:20,867
I might even be able to seal
your spiritual power.

39
00:03:20,867 --> 00:03:24,079
But "sealing" your power
should not equal "death".

40
00:03:24,663 --> 00:03:27,165
If you hadn't chosen death yourself.

41
00:03:28,709 --> 00:03:30,127
With that being said...

42
00:03:32,879 --> 00:03:37,342
Just forget about your ex-boyfriend
and switch to me,

43
00:03:37,802 --> 00:03:38,812
Mio.

44
00:03:48,395 --> 00:03:52,065
What's with that?
It doesn't suit you at all, Shido.

45
00:03:52,065 --> 00:03:54,985
I mean, are you even serious?

46
00:03:54,985 --> 00:03:57,821
W-Whether it suits me or not...

47
00:03:57,821 --> 00:03:59,072
I'm serious!

48
00:03:59,072 --> 00:04:01,867
I'm seriously going
to take you away from Shinji!

49
00:04:03,461 --> 00:04:04,585
I see.

50
00:04:05,912 --> 00:04:07,330
That's what he said.

51
00:04:07,330 --> 00:04:09,499
So, what will you do, Shin?

52
00:04:09,499 --> 00:04:11,835
Do you want me to say something?

53
00:04:12,335 --> 00:04:15,839
I'm just someone who is
detached from Shido's memory.

54
00:04:15,839 --> 00:04:18,884
A phony of a phony, you know?

55
00:04:18,884 --> 00:04:23,054
But it's Shin's memory, right?

56
00:04:23,054 --> 00:04:24,139
Just say it.

57
00:04:24,139 --> 00:04:28,393
Because what you think should be
the same as the real Shin.

58
00:04:29,102 --> 00:04:32,022
Otherwise, I might be taken
by Shido, you know?

59
00:04:33,770 --> 00:04:34,865
Oh, well.

60
00:04:36,693 --> 00:04:38,528
Then, let me say this in return.

61
00:04:39,488 --> 00:04:41,782
Don't mess with me, idiot!

62
00:04:41,782 --> 00:04:44,701
You just saying whatever you want
when others keep their mouths shut!

63
00:04:44,701 --> 00:04:46,495
I can't stand it, even if you were me!

64
00:04:47,120 --> 00:04:49,915
I will never...

65
00:04:49,915 --> 00:04:52,918
give Mio to you!

66
00:04:55,045 --> 00:04:58,381
Well, this is how I felt before I died.

67
00:04:59,090 --> 00:05:00,133
It's just...

68
00:05:00,634 --> 00:05:02,344
I'm already a goner, right?

69
00:05:04,888 --> 00:05:10,060
Honestly, the thought of Mio choosing
someone other than me makes my heart burst.

70
00:05:10,977 --> 00:05:14,564
But even so, I don't want Mio
to choose her own death.

71
00:05:15,649 --> 00:05:19,528
There were still many things in this world
that I wanted to show to Mio.

72
00:05:22,572 --> 00:05:24,074
This sea is beautiful.

73
00:05:24,741 --> 00:05:27,911
I am so glad I was able
to bring Mio here.

74
00:05:28,954 --> 00:05:32,791
But it's time to go somewhere else.

75
00:05:34,042 --> 00:05:35,377
I'm sorry, Mio.

76
00:05:36,211 --> 00:05:38,630
I've been holding you back
for a long time now.

77
00:05:44,522 --> 00:05:45,679
Mio...

78
00:05:46,721 --> 00:05:49,641
Shido... I...

79
00:05:51,309 --> 00:05:52,894
W-What's happening?!

80
00:05:52,894 --> 00:05:54,688
Reine, is this...

81
00:05:54,688 --> 00:05:56,606
