83
00:05:58,900 --> 00:06:00,527
Spirit Formula?

84
00:06:01,027 --> 00:06:03,613
This is the formula
that once created the spirit,

85
00:06:03,613 --> 00:06:06,575
or in other words,
my existence, in this world.

86
00:06:06,575 --> 00:06:08,243
It's the secret art of witchcraft.

87
00:06:09,077 --> 00:06:13,540
As far as I know,
only Westcott can do this.

88
00:06:13,540 --> 00:06:15,083
Hold on!

89
00:06:15,083 --> 00:06:19,588
Are you saying that a new spirit is
being created out there right now?

90
00:06:19,588 --> 00:06:20,881
Looks like it.

91
00:06:21,673 --> 00:06:23,758
A Spirit of Origin like me.

92
00:06:24,799 --> 00:06:28,638
Moreover, it seems that Westcott is
at the center of that power.

93
00:06:29,306 --> 00:06:33,810
Apparently, he is trying to perform
the formula using himself as the core.

94
00:06:34,477 --> 00:06:39,858
Does that mean that Westcott will get
the power of Spirit of Origin?

95
00:06:39,858 --> 00:06:41,484
The same power as Mio?

96
00:06:42,125 --> 00:06:43,364
Yes.

97
00:06:43,365 --> 00:06:48,241
Now a huge flow of spiritual power
has appeared here, which is me.

98
00:06:48,992 --> 00:06:53,872
Westcott intends to use this flow
to make himself the Spirit of Origin.

99
00:06:55,040 --> 00:06:59,252
Now he no longer
needs the ten Sephira.

100
00:06:59,794 --> 00:07:03,506
He can just use the power
that appears here.

101
00:07:03,506 --> 00:07:07,177
Could it be that Westcott
had planned this all along―

102
00:07:07,677 --> 00:07:08,762
Perhaps.

103
00:07:08,762 --> 00:07:12,140
He must have known
about this situation beforehand.

104
00:07:12,682 --> 00:07:14,184
It's my fault...

105
00:07:14,184 --> 00:07:17,771
Because of what I went through in the future,
he knew about it from Beelzebub.

106
00:07:17,771 --> 00:07:20,649
No, if you're talking about the cause,

107
00:07:20,649 --> 00:07:23,151
it's entirely my fault.

108
00:07:23,151 --> 00:07:27,447
Besides, now is not
the time for regrets, right?

109
00:07:27,447 --> 00:07:28,531
That's right!

110
00:07:29,199 --> 00:07:32,118
I don't want to be taken
advantage of by that guy,

111
00:07:32,118 --> 00:07:35,538
and I don't want my world of
memories with Shin to be remade.

112
00:07:36,283 --> 00:07:38,399
Shido, lend me your strength.

113
00:07:39,042 --> 00:07:42,754
It may sound strange coming
from me who killed the spirits

114
00:07:42,754 --> 00:07:44,965
