149
00:09:33,531 --> 00:09:35,075
Ain Soph!

150
00:09:44,709 --> 00:09:45,835
Mio!

151
00:09:45,835 --> 00:09:47,337
It won't last long!

152
00:09:47,337 --> 00:09:50,715
Everyone, please, help me out!

153
00:09:50,715 --> 00:09:54,344
I met Shin to protect this world!

154
00:09:57,758 --> 00:09:58,772
This is...

155
00:10:04,020 --> 00:10:05,772
