158
00:10:11,111 --> 00:10:15,406
We will have to combine
our strengths to defeat him.

159
00:10:15,406 --> 00:10:18,409
Combine our strengths?

160
00:10:18,409 --> 00:10:20,203
Is that even possible?

161
00:10:20,953 --> 00:10:22,997
