created by Beelzebub.

186
00:12:22,784 --> 00:12:27,080
Then there is no reason why
we can't do the same with Rasiel!

187
00:12:27,080 --> 00:12:31,334
Of course, individuals exposed to
Athiel's power cannot be revived.

188
00:12:31,334 --> 00:12:32,710
With this body,

189
00:12:32,710 --> 00:12:36,339
