Michael!

203
00:13:12,875 --> 00:13:14,043
Haniel!

204
00:13:14,794 --> 00:13:15,878
Raphael!

205
00:13:16,963 --> 00:13:18,006
Gabriel!

206
00:13:18,923 --> 00:13:20,341
Sandalphon!

207
00:13:23,970 --> 00:13:26,032
Go, Shido!

208
00:13:26,033 --> 00:13:26,973
Yes!

209
00:13:27,223 --> 00:13:29,017
Shido Itsuka!

210
00:13:54,125 --> 00:13:55,417
Well done,

211
00:13:55,960 --> 00:13:57,420
Shido Itsuka.

212
00:13:58,504 --> 00:14:02,133
