the world more to you, Mio!

228
00:14:53,309 --> 00:14:55,186
But, why?!

229
00:14:57,105 --> 00:15:00,608
Shido, you are really nice.

230
00:15:01,109 --> 00:15:02,985
I love you so much.

231
00:15:04,654 --> 00:15:07,615
However... after Shin,

232
00:15:08,382 --> 00:15:09,397
okay?

233
00:15:12,578 --> 00:15:18,501
