258
00:17:25,836 --> 00:17:27,129
Shin...

259
00:17:27,129 --> 00:17:29,382
Shin! Shin!

260
00:17:29,382 --> 00:17:30,590
Mio!

261
00:17:30,591 --> 00:17:33,135
