00:18:00,955 --> 00:18:03,291
I'll get you to
a Medical Realizer right away...

269
00:18:03,291 --> 00:18:04,625
It's futile.

270
00:18:05,293 --> 00:18:10,673
I caught up in the annihilation of Angel
and Demon King at point-blank range.

271
00:18:11,299 --> 00:18:14,427
It's a wonder I'm still conscious.

272
00:18:15,678 --> 00:18:16,762
Ike...

273
00:18:19,231 --> 00:18:21,609
Ah, Elliot...

274
00:18:22,331 --> 00:18:23,811
And Karen.

275
00:18:25,479 --> 00:18:28,316
I beg you, Elliot. Save Ike!

276
00:18:28,316 --> 00:18:29,817
You could do it, right?!

277
00:18:30,610 --> 00:18:31,629
Elliot...

278
00:18:32,612 --> 00:18:34,572
If only I could.

279
00:18:34,572 --> 00:18:36,616
However, he is...

280
00:18:42,747 --> 00:18:45,041
Why did you bother to come here?

281
00:18:45,583 --> 00:18:48,085
Are you here to laugh at me?

282
00:18:48,085 --> 00:18:53,966
Is it so strange to want to see
a friend on his deathbed?

283
00:18:54,507 --> 00:18:58,594
Yeah, it was a dumb question...

284
00:18:58,596 --> 00:19:01,891
We may have taken different paths,

285
00:19:01,891 --> 00:19:04,477
but you and Karen are my friends...

286
00:19:05,061 --> 00:19:06,228
Besides...

287
00:19:07,063 --> 00:19:10,107
We were both dumped by the same woman.

288
00:19:12,735 --> 00:19:13,986
I can't say you're wrong.

289
00:19:25,331 --> 00:19:26,624
<i>What?</i>

290
00:19:28,334 --> 00:19:31,462
<i>I didn't realize how easy it was...</i>

291
00:19:45,643 --> 00:19:47,890
Shido. Shido!

292
00:19:51,899 --> 00:19:53,192
Shido!

293
00:19:53,192 --> 00:19:57,363
Mhm... You're awake now.
We were worried about you.

294
00:19:57,363 --> 00:20:00,116
Relief. Kaguya was so worried that

295
00:20:00,116 --> 00:20:02,785
she was crying and
hanging on to Shido.

296
00:20:02,785 --> 00:20:04,787
I didn't go that far!

297
00:20:04,787 --> 00:20:06,914
Tohka... how's Mio?

298
00:20:13,458 --> 00:20:15,384
I... see...

299
00:20:20,219 --> 00:20:23,472
Aw, I've been dumped.

300
00:20:23,472 --> 00:20:25,391
She prefers Shin rather than me.

301
00:20:26,392 --> 00:20:27,643
Is that so?

302
00:20:27,643 --> 00:20:29,562
Then, we can't do anything about that.

303
00:20:30,187 --> 00:20:34,400
I guess even Shido couldn't stand up
to the true love couple.

304
00:20:38,695 --> 00:20:39,447
Huh?

305
00:21:23,240 --> 00:21:24,366
You've...

306
00:21:25,034 --> 00:21:27,203
You've met Shin, huh,

307
00:21:28,433 --> 00:21:29,466
Mio?

308
00:21:45,930 --> 00:21:46,946
Shido!

309
00:21:49,892 --> 00:21:52,228
Sorry I'm late, Shido.

310
00:21:53,248 --> 00:21:54,788
I just got here, too.

311
00:21:54,789 --> 00:21:59,944
<i>As far as my eyes can see,
colors abound</i>

312
00:21:59,944 --> 00:22:05,825
<i>Scenes of the past, unravel, unwound</i>

313
00:22:05,825 --> 00:22:11,247
<i>Paradox tightens,
the resolve we've found</i>

314
00:22:11,247 --> 00:22:16,627
<i>Sinking into tomorrows,
out of bounds</i>

315
00:22:17,294 --> 00:22:23,133
<i>If I open these hands,
once clenched tight</i>

316
00:22:23,133 --> 00:22:31,016
<i>I'll grasp at hopes,
long lost from sight</i>

317
00:22:31,016 --> 00:22:37,189
<i>Tears have dried,
facing the darkest night</i>

318
00:22:37,189 --> 00:22:43,362
<i>Even as you gaze at a future bright</i>

319
00:22:43,362 --> 00:22:48,826
<i>Finally, the light, almost within sight</i>

320
00:22:48,826 --> 00:22:52,705
<i>No words needed,
in silence, take flight</i>

321
00:22:52,705 --> 00:22:57,459
<i>For all the answers, here,</i>

322
00:22:57,459 --> 00:23:04,008
<i>in our hands alight</i>

323
00:23:15,728 --> 00:23:17,521
Now, Shido...

324
00:23:18,071 --> 00:23:19,560
Let's start our date!

